"Ehraam-e-Junoon" follows the story of a young and immensely beautiful girl named Shanzay, who is filled with pride and stubbornness due to her upper-class upbringing. Shanzay believes that money can buy everything, including happiness. 

Despite her high standards, Shanzay is yet to find a man who can impress her until she meets Shayan at an event. Shayan is a handsome young man from a middle-class family, who takes up a job as a pizza delivery boy to make ends meet. Shanzay who is immediately drawn to Shayan wants to provide him with a better lifestyle however, Shayan keeps his distance and refuses to accept any of Shanzayâ€™s advances.

As the story unfolds, Shanzay and Shayan's paths cross again and again, and Shanzay begins to question her beliefs about love and money. Will Shayan be the one to break through Shanzay's walls of pride and stubbornness, or will she continue to chase after superficial things?

The drama serial "Ehraam-e-Junoon" promises to take viewers on a rollercoaster ride of emotions as it explores the themes of love, pride, and class differences.

"Ehraam-e-Junoon" follows the story of a young and immensely beautiful girl named Shanzay, who is filled with pride and stubbornness due to her upper-class upbringing. Shanzay believes that money can buy everything, including happiness. 

Despite her high standards, Shanzay is yet to find a man who can impress her until she meets Shayan at an event. Shayan is a handsome young man from a middle-class family, who takes up a job as a pizza delivery boy to make ends meet. Shanzay who is immediately drawn to Shayan wants to provide him with a better lifestyle however, Shayan keeps his distance and refuses to accept any of Shanzayâ€™s advances.

As the story unfolds, Shanzay and Shayan's paths cross again and again, and Shanzay begins to question her beliefs about love and money. Will Shayan be the one to break through Shanzay's walls of pride and stubbornness, or will she continue to chase after superficial things?

The drama serial "Ehraam-e-Junoon" promises to take viewers on a rollercoaster ride of emotions as it explores the themes of love, pride, and class differences.

snippet.title: Coke Studio Bharat | Kya Karie Korimol | ALIF x Aashima Mahajan x Noor Mohammad
snippet.description:
A father-daughter relationship envelops immense compassion, protection, and love. They share a special connection that grows stronger with time and never fades away. #KyaKarieKorimol unveils such a beautiful father-daughter bond on a wedding day. The lyrics tell the emotional journey of a bride and her father as they prepare for her wedding feast.

Featuring Alif, a poet, singer, and songwriter who won the IRAA Award for his single â€˜Like A Sufiâ€™, his poignant and melancholic lyrical compositions are known for their colloquial references to society.

Heâ€™s accompanied by the very soulful Aashima Mahajan, a well-known Indian musician, playback singer, and actor & Noor Mohammad, an Indian traditional Sufi music performer and songwriter from Handwara in North Kashmir.

Tune in to this masterpiece to get a glimpse of a father-daughter love.

The lyrics tell the emotional journey of a bride and her father as they prepare for her wedding feast.

Featuring Alif, a poet, singer, and songwriter who won the IRAA Award for his single â€˜Like A Sufiâ€™, his poignant and melancholic lyrical compositions are known for their colloquial references to society.

Heâ€™s accompanied by the very soulful Aashima Mahajan, a well-known Indian musician, playback singer, and actor & Noor Mohammad, an Indian traditional Sufi music performer and songwriter from Handwara in North Kashmir.

Tune in to this masterpiece to get a glimpse of a father-daughter love.

Tere Bin Episode 49 Teaser - 25th May 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerabâ€™s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her familyâ€™s decision regarding her and Murtasimâ€™s life. Meerabâ€™s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerabâ€™s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasimâ€™s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

--------------------------------------------------------
Popatlal, or Pyaarelal, receives a phone call from Anjali, who informs him that she has wonderful news concerning his marriage. Pyaarelal hurries to meet Anjali at Gokuldham Society. When he arrives at Anjali's residence, he notices that other Gokuldham females are present. Anjali informs him about her cousin Nanda Kaki, who has a niece named Sapna and is looking for a groom. Pyaarelal is ecstatic after hearing the news and wants to see Sapna and her family right away. Anjali informs Pyaarelal that Sapna and her family will come at 5 in the evening. Pyaarelal now persuades Taarak to attend the gathering, but Taarak informs him that his boss may not grant him an early leave owing to work pressure.

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalalâ€™s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in 'Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance, as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

snippet.title: Divya, IAS, Rank 105 | UPSC Topper 2022  | Hindi Medium | Mock Interview | Drishti IAS
snippet.description:
Divya has secured 105th rank in UPSC CSE exam 2022. The mock interview she has given in Drishti IAS institute has been uploaded on Drishti IAS Channel. We extend our heartiest congratulations to Divya on this great achievement. We feel immense pleasure to be a part of her beautiful journey and once again we wish her all the very best for a bright future.
As we all know that UPSC CSE Mock Interviews are a great medium to understand the various dimensions of the Personality Test conducted by UPSC. These Mock Interviews not only familiarize the aspirants with the actual process of UPSC Interviews but also help in identifying the areas that a candidate needs to work upon. Even though one can imagine oneself in a UPSC Interview setting, it is strongly recommended that you watch these Mock Interviews and learn from the experiences of IAS toppers, so that you give your best shot when you reach the interview stage of examination.
We hope that this video of the UPSC IAS Mock Interview will help you understand the approach one should have to tackle the various kinds of questions asked by the panel members.

localized.title: Divya, IAS, Rank 105 | UPSC Topper 2022  | Hindi Medium | Mock Interview | Drishti IAS
localized.description:
Divya has secured 105th rank in UPSC CSE exam 2022. The mock interview she has given in Drishti IAS institute has been uploaded on Drishti IAS Channel. We extend our heartiest congratulations to Divya on this great achievement. We feel immense pleasure to be a part of her beautiful journey and once again we wish her all the very best for a bright future.
As we all know that UPSC CSE Mock Interviews are a great medium to understand the various dimensions of the Personality Test conducted by UPSC. These Mock Interviews not only familiarize the aspirants with the actual process of UPSC Interviews but also help in identifying the areas that a candidate needs to work upon. Even though one can imagine oneself in a UPSC Interview setting, it is strongly recommended that you watch these Mock Interviews and learn from the experiences of IAS toppers, so that you give your best shot when you reach the interview stage of examination.

snippet.title: PART 2 - RAHUL DUA IN AMERICA | The HORRORS of RENTING a CAR in USA | StandUp Comedy by Rahul Dua
snippet.description:
"Oh Hello!" Australia and NZ tour (Jun'23) tickets: https://linktr.ee/RahulDuaTour
"New Comedy Special 2023-24" UK-EU Tour (Aug-Sep'23) tickets: https://linktr.ee/RahulDuaTour

This video is the 2nd and the most important part of my series of jokes and observations about life in USA. 
These are observational jokes rehearsed and delivered in just 8 - 9 shows, unlike conventional stand up content which takes a couple of years to perfect. 
Since public transport is nearly absent in USA, I had to rent a car to move around. Though bad, it was the one way. This video is a real life personal account of me renting American Muscle and the horrors associated with it. Via this video I hope to convey all of my anger, surprise, shock, regret and the plethora of other emotions that I felt arising out of the massive inconvenience and hidden charges associated with US Car rental. 
Drop in a LIKE and SHARE the video if you've had similar experiences or know someone who went through something similar, and COMMENT with your favourite joke from the video. 

#rahuldua #usa #standupcomedy #nri #comedy #jokes #carrental #taxes #dodge #americanmuscle #story

Gerwig directed â€œBarbieâ€ from a screenplay by Gerwig & Oscar nominee Noah Baumbach (â€œMarriage Story,â€ â€œThe Squid and the Whaleâ€), based on Barbie by Mattel.  The filmâ€™s producers are Oscar nominee David Heyman (â€œMarriage Story,â€ â€œGravityâ€), Robbie, Tom Ackerley and Robbie Brenner, with Gerwig, Baumbach, Ynon Kreiz, Richard Dickson, Michael Sharp, Josey McNamara, Courtenay Valenti, Toby Emmerich and Cate Adams serving as executive producers.

Gerwigâ€™s creative team behind the camera included Oscar-nominated director of photography Rodrigo Prieto (â€œThe Irishman,â€ â€œSilence,â€ â€œBrokeback Mountainâ€), six-time Oscar-nominated production designer Sarah Greenwood (â€œBeauty and the Beast,â€ â€œAnna Kareninaâ€), editor Nick Houy (â€œLittle Women,â€ â€œLady Birdâ€), Oscar-winning costume designer Jacqueline Durran (â€œLittle Women,â€ â€œAnna Kareninaâ€), visual effects supervisor Glen Pratt (â€œPaddington 2,â€ â€œBeauty and the Beastâ€) and music supervisor George Drakoulias (â€œWhite Noise,â€ â€œMarriage Storyâ€), with music by Oscar winners Mark Ronson and Andrew Wyatt (â€œA Star Is Bornâ€).

Warner Bros. Pictures Presents a Heyday Films Production, a LuckyChap Entertainment Production, a NB/GG Pictures Production, a Mattel Production, â€œBarbie.â€  The film will be distributed worldwide by Warner Bros. Pictures and released in theaters only nationwide on July 21, 2023 and beginning internationally on July 19, 2023.

Mass Maharaja Ravi Teja and Vamseeâ€™s Pan India Project #TigerNageswaraRao to be produced by Abhishek Agarwal under Abhishek Agarwal Arts and to be presented by Tej Narayan Agarwal.

Tiger Nageswara Rao will be made in Telugu, Hindi, Tamil, Kannada, and Malayalam languages. Based on the life of the notorious thief from Stuartpuram, Tiger Nageswara Rao is going to be highest budgeted film for Ravi Teja. This will mark first Pan India project of the actor.

GV Prakash Kumar will score muic for the film that has dialogues by Srikanth Vissa. R Madhie ISC will crank the camera and Avinash Kolla is the production designer. Mayank Singhaniya is the co-producer.
